The scripts in this directory can be run as follows:

1) Common setup

  $ MYPATH=$(basename /PATH/TO/DIR/CONTAINING/git_fast_filter.py)
  $ export PYTHONPATH=MYPATH:$PYTHONPATH

2a) Running the individual scripts, case a:

  $ mkdir target_dir
  $ cd target_dir
  $ git init
  $ (cd source_repo && git fast-export --all) | $SCRIPT_NAME | git fast-import

  where $SNRIPT_NAME is one of commit_info.py, file_filter.py,
  rename_master_to_slave.py, or strip-cvs-keywords.py

2b) Running the individual scripts, case b:

  $ $SCRIPT_NAME source_repo target_nonexistent_dir

  where $SNRIPT_NAME is print_progress.py
